name: R&R (Rest and Relaxation)
description: What? The screwy warp terminal has sent you to hell instead of Earth for a long awaited R&R, no ammo, no armor, no friends; so what else is new? Mission: recon the area, stay alive, and report your findings to the COC(Combat Operations Center). BTW.. NO tricks or traps in any of my maps, there is always a way out.
